Title: Sewing string tree vertices with ghosts

Authors: L. Sandoval Jr

Comments: LaTeX, 26 pages, 19 figures

Journal-ref: Braz.J.Phys. 32 (2002) 232-254

It is shown how to sew string vertices with ghosts at tree level in order toproduce new tree vertices using the Group Theoretic approach to String Theory.It is then verified the BRST invariance of the sewn vertex and shown that ithas the correct ghost number.